        "liquid": "<style>\n  .sj-ing {\n    background-color: #ffffff;\n    padding: 80px 20px 60px;\n    font-family: 'Georgia', 'Times New Roman', serif;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__header {\n    text-align: center;\n    max-width: 660px;\n    margin: 0 auto 56px;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__eyebrow {\n    display: block;\n    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 4px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #8A4B2D;\n    margin-bottom: 14px;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__title {\n    font-size: clamp(24px, 3.5vw, 38px);\n    font-weight: normal;\n    color: #8A4B2D;\n    line-height: 1.25;\n    margin: 0 0 14px;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__subtitle {\n    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 15px;\n    color: #9a7060;\n    font-style: italic;\n    margin: 0;\n    line-height: 1.65;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__ornament {\n    display: flex;\n    align-items: center;\n    gap: 14px;\n    max-width: 280px;\n    margin: 24px auto 0;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__ornament::before,\n  .sj-ing__ornament::after {\n    content: '';\n    flex: 1;\n    height: 1px;\n    background: linear-gradient(to right, transparent, #8A4B2D, transparent);\n  }\n  .sj-ing__ornament span { color: #8A4B2D; font-size: 13px; }\n\n  .sj-ing__group {\n    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 10px;\n    letter-spacing: 4px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #8A4B2D;\n    margin: 0 auto 18px;\n    padding-bottom: 10px;\n    border-bottom: 1px solid #F0E2D8;\n    max-width: 580px;\n  }\n\n  .sj-ing__grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, 1fr);\n    gap: 18px;\n    max-width: 580px;\n    margin: 0 auto 44px;\n  }\n\n  .sj-ing__card {\n    background: #ffffff;\n    border-radius: 18px;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    border: 1.5px solid #F0E2D8;\n    box-shadow: 0 2px 18px rgba(138,75,45,0.07);\n    transition: transform 0.32s ease, box-shadow 0.32s ease, border-color 0.32s ease;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__card:hover {\n    transform: translateY(-6px);\n    box-shadow: 0 12px 36px rgba(138,75,45,0.14);\n    border-color: #8A4B2D;\n  }\n\n  .sj-ing__visual {\n    width: 100%;\n    aspect-ratio: 1 / 1;\n    overflow: hidden;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__visual img {\n    width: 100%;\n    height: 100%;\n    object-fit: cover;\n    display: block;\n    transition: transform 0.4s ease;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__card:hover .sj-ing__visual img {\n    transform: scale(1.05);\n  }\n\n  .sj-ing__body {\n    padding: 18px 18px 20px;\n    border-top: 1px solid #F5E9E0;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__inci {\n    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 9px;\n    letter-spacing: 1.2px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #b8825c;\n    margin-bottom: 5px;\n    white-space: nowrap;\n    overflow: hidden;\n    text-overflow: ellipsis;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__name {\n    font-size: 16px;\n    font-weight: bold;\n    color: #8A4B2D;\n    margin-bottom: 9px;\n    line-height: 1.2;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__benefit {\n    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #7a6050;\n    line-height: 1.65;\n    margin-bottom: 13px;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__tags { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: 6px; }\n  .sj-ing__tag {\n    display: inline-block;\n    background: #F5EDE7;\n    color: #8A4B2D;\n    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 10px;\n    padding: 3px 10px;\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    letter-spacing: 0.4px;\n    border: 1px solid #F0E2D8;\n  }\n\n  .sj-ing__banner {\n    max-width: 1160px;\n    margin: 0 auto;\n    background: linear-gradient(135deg, #4a2415 0%, #8A4B2D 50%, #a86540 100%);\n    border-radius: 20px;\n    padding: 44px 48px;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__banner-title {\n    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 11px;\n    letter-spacing: 3.5px;\n    text-transform: uppercase;\n    color: #f9dcc8;\n    text-align: center;\n    margin-bottom: 28px;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__banner-grid {\n    display: grid;\n    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);\n    gap: 20px;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__banner-item { display: flex; gap: 12px; align-items: flex-start; }\n  .sj-ing__banner-dot {\n    width: 6px; height: 6px;\n    border-radius: 50%;\n    background: #f9dcc8;\n    margin-top: 7px;\n    flex-shrink: 0;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__banner-text {\n    font-family: 'Trebuchet MS', sans-serif;\n    font-size: 13px;\n    color: #f7e6da;\n    line-height: 1.6;\n  }\n  .sj-ing__banner-text strong { color: #f9dcc8; display: block; margin-bottom: 2px; }\n\n  @media (max-width: 768px) {\n    .sj-ing { padding: 48px 0 48px; }\n    .sj-ing__header { padding: 0 20px; }\n    .sj-ing__group  { margin: 0 20px 18px; }\n\n    .sj-ing__grid {\n      display: flex;\n      flex-wrap: nowrap;\n      overflow-x: auto;\n      scroll-snap-type: x mandatory;\n      -webkit-overflow-scrolling: touch;\n      gap: 14px;\n      padding: 4px 20px 16px;\n      margin: 0 0 44px;\n      max-width: 100%;\n      scrollbar-width: none;\n      -ms-overflow-style: none;\n    }\n    .sj-ing__grid::-webkit-scrollbar { display: none; }\n\n    .sj-ing__card {\n      min-width: 75vw;\n      max-width: 75vw;\n      scroll-snap-align: start;\n    }\n\n    .sj-ing__banner {\n      margin: 0 20px;\n      padding: 28px 20px;\n    }\n    .sj-ing__banner-grid { grid-template-columns: 1fr; }\n  }\n</style>\n\n<section class=\"sj-ing\">\n\n  <div class=\"sj-ing__header\">\n    <span class=\"sj-ing__eyebrow\">Formule 100% d&eacute;taill&eacute;e</span>\n    <h2 class=\"sj-ing__title\">Nos Actifs &amp; Leurs Bienfaits</h2>\n    <p class=\"sj-ing__subtitle\">Quatre actifs, choisis pour agir &agrave; la racine &mdash; pas une liste &agrave; rallonge.</p>\n    <div class=\"sj-ing__ornament\"><span>&#10022;</span></div>\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- GROUPE 1 -- Pour un cuir chevelu apaisé -->\n  <p class=\"sj-ing__group\">&#127807; &nbsp; Pour un cuir chevelu apais&eacute;</p>\n  <div class=\"sj-ing__grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"sj-ing__card\">\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__visual\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1008/1550/3744/files/4_551cb5a1-8b33-4603-9417-53420295581e.png?v=1784903800\" alt=\"Romarin\">\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__body\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__inci\">Rosmarinus Officinalis Leaf Oil</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__name\">Romarin</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__benefit\">Utilis&eacute; depuis longtemps pour stimuler la circulation du cuir chevelu et soutenir les follicules &mdash; un terrain plus r&eacute;ceptif &agrave; la pousse.</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__tags\">\n          <span class=\"sj-ing__tag\">Circulation</span>\n          <span class=\"sj-ing__tag\">Cuir chevelu</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"sj-ing__card\">\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__visual\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1008/1550/3744/files/3_af96c4f8-59c9-4be7-b96c-5e97f5cbee1a.png?v=1784903800\" alt=\"Nettoyant aux acides amin&eacute;s\">\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__body\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__inci\">Tensioactifs doux (base acide amin&eacute;)</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__name\">Nettoyant aux Acides Amin&eacute;s</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__benefit\">Plut&ocirc;t qu'un nettoyant agressif, cette base douce &eacute;limine les impuret&eacute;s tout en limitant l'irritation et la s&eacute;cheresse.</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__tags\">\n          <span class=\"sj-ing__tag\">Sans sulfates</span>\n          <span class=\"sj-ing__tag\">Douceur</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- GROUPE 2 -- Pour une fibre plus forte et plus dense -->\n  <p class=\"sj-ing__group\">&#10024; &nbsp; Pour une fibre plus forte et plus dense</p>\n  <div class=\"sj-ing__grid\">\n\n    <div class=\"sj-ing__card\">\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__visual\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1008/1550/3744/files/2_deb20363-e935-4909-a33e-0ce6e60578ca.png?v=1784903800\" alt=\"K&eacute;ratine hydrolys&eacute;e\">\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__body\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__inci\">Hydrolyzed Keratin</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__name\">K&eacute;ratine Hydrolys&eacute;e</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__benefit\">Une prot&eacute;ine qui vient combler et renforcer la fibre capillaire de l'int&eacute;rieur, pour r&eacute;duire la casse et redonner de la tenue.</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__tags\">\n          <span class=\"sj-ing__tag\">Renfort</span>\n          <span class=\"sj-ing__tag\">Anti-casse</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n    <div class=\"sj-ing__card\">\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__visual\">\n        <img src=\"https://cdn.shopify.com/s/files/1/1008/1550/3744/files/1_3cbc95c5-dde3-4c26-b2e3-5dfca493c563.png?v=1784903800\" alt=\"Biotine\">\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__body\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__inci\">Biotin (Vitamine B7)</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__name\">Biotine</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__benefit\">La vitamine capillaire la plus reconnue&nbsp;: elle soutient la production de k&eacute;ratine &agrave; la racine et accompagne une chevelure d'apparence plus dense.</div>\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__tags\">\n          <span class=\"sj-ing__tag\">Densit&eacute;</span>\n          <span class=\"sj-ing__tag\">Racine</span>\n        </div>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n\n  </div>\n\n  <!-- BANNER RÉSUMÉ -->\n  <div class=\"sj-ing__banner\">\n    <p class=\"sj-ing__banner-title\">&#10022; &nbsp; Ce que Soin Jade fait pour vous &nbsp; &#10022;</p>\n    <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-grid\">\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-item\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-dot\"></div>\n        <p class=\"sj-ing__banner-text\"><strong>Stimule la circulation</strong> du cuir chevelu, gr&acirc;ce au romarin</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-item\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-dot\"></div>\n        <p class=\"sj-ing__banner-text\"><strong>Nettoie sans agresser</strong>, m&ecirc;me les cuirs chevelus sensibles</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-item\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-dot\"></div>\n        <p class=\"sj-ing__banner-text\"><strong>Renforce la fibre</strong> gr&acirc;ce &agrave; la k&eacute;ratine hydrolys&eacute;e</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-item\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-dot\"></div>\n        <p class=\"sj-ing__banner-text\"><strong>Soutient la densit&eacute;</strong> &agrave; la racine, avec un usage r&eacute;gulier</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-item\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-dot\"></div>\n        <p class=\"sj-ing__banner-text\"><strong>Une seule routine</strong>, pas trois produits &agrave; jongler</p>\n      </div>\n      <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-item\">\n        <div class=\"sj-ing__banner-dot\"></div>\n        <p class=\"sj-ing__banner-text\"><strong>Formule 100% transparente</strong>, rien cach&eacute; derri&egrave;re \"fragrance\"</p>\n      </div>\n    </div>\n  </div>\n\n</section>",
